title: Kwest - The Vault (2015) [Electronic, Trap, Dubstep, EDM, IDM]
description:
Thank you so much friends and fans for stopping by today to download "The Vault" from Canadian electronic artist Kwest. We hope you will be enthusiastically surprised with the results from this artist hailing from the land that has brought greats such as Deadmau5, Datsik, Adventure Club, Keys N Krates and so many more. His three year journey into sound manipulation has just begun, as his foray into the genres of Dubstep, Trap, House, Ambient, Classical and Hip-hop have only started to come to fruition.

14 songs span these genres on the main album, but more importantly than all the buzz terms we hear like "BPM", "genres" or "EDM", this album straddles many emotions, leading you through the brightest to darkest of days. Additionally, there are four more songs located in the vault backroom, they did not quite make the album cut, but are no less worth the listen, along with an album cover for EVERY song on the album, and several HD wallpapers too. 
Thanks again for downloading this and sharing the word. I look forward to feedback from any of you, please don't hesitate friends and fans.
